OL,5,
OL,6,CG1980FThe first experimental
OL,7,F"in-vision" transmission of a selection
OL,8,Fof Ceefax pages airs on BBC One, 8.30am
OL,9,F- 9am. The text-based digest of news,
OL,10,Fsport, travel, weather and TV/radio
OL,11,Flistings would become a regular fixture
OL,12,Fin the daytime schedules for a number
OL,13,Fof years, particularly on BBC Two.
